      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Aptos,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Which enzyme is common to the synthesis pathways of both ketone bodies and cholesterol? </span></span></span></p>",
